@startuml DailyRobotClassification_DatabaseFlow
title Daily Robot Classification - Database Flow (AI + TW)

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam databaseBackgroundColor #E8F5E9
skinparam databaseBorderColor #4CAF50
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam noteBorderColor #FBC02D
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam activityBorderColor #1976D2

|JobService|
start

split
  
  note right: **AI Robot Detection Flow**
  |AI Robot Service|
  :Start();
  
  :GetRobotDetections(RobotDetection_LastID);
  
  |CTS_DataCenter (MySQL)|
  :Read System Parameter: RobotDetection_LastID;
  
  :Execute SP: **CTS_DC_RobotDetection_GetLatest**;
  note right
    **Database**: CTS_DataCenter.ctsService
    **Timeout**: 300 seconds (default)
    
    **Purpose**: Get AI-detected robot customers
    **Input**: @ip_RobotDetectionLastID (long)
    
    **Query Logic**:
    ```sql
    SELECT 
      RobotDetectionID,
      CustID,
      CategoryID,
      LastModifiedDate
    FROM RobotDetection
    WHERE RobotDetectionID > @ip_RobotDetectionLastID
    ORDER BY RobotDetectionID
    LIMIT (batch size)
    ```
    
    **Data Source**: AI/ML Robot Detection System ⭐
    - Automated pattern detection
    - ML model predictions
    - Continuous monitoring
    
    **Returns**: RobotAIEntity[]
  end note
  
  :Return RobotAIEntity[];
  
  |AI Robot Service|
  if (Has robots?) then (yes)
    :Chunk by internalSize;
    
    repeat
      :Transform to InsertProblemAccountEntity;
      
      :InsertProblemAccountPackage();
      |CTS_DataCenter (MySQL)|
      :INSERT INTO CTSCustomerClassification;
      note right
        **Insert Robot PA**:
        - CustID, CategoryID (Robot)
        - FunctionId: RobotUserJob
        - CCInputFlow: InsertPACategory
        - Robot-specific fields
      end note
      
      :Return Inserted CustIDs;
      
      |AI Robot Service|
      :PushExternalPackageByCustId();
      |External - MainDB|
      :Push to MainDB API;
      note right
        **External Push**:
        - RoleGroup: Member
        - IsUpdateDangerToMainDB: true
        - IsSyncAFCData: false (no AFC for robots)
      end note
      
      |AI Robot Service|
      :Thread.Sleep(throttle);
      
    repeat while (More chunks?) is (yes)
    -> no;
    
    |CTS_DataCenter (MySQL)|
    :Update System Parameter: RobotDetection_LastID;
    note right
      ```sql
      UPDATE CTS_SystemParameter
      SET Value = MAX(RobotDetectionID)
      WHERE ParameterKey = 'RobotDetection_LastID'
      ```
    end note
  endif

split again

  note right: **TW Robot Flow**
  |TW Robot Service|
  :Start();
  
  :GetLastTimespan();
  |CTS_DataCenter (MySQL)|
  :Read System Parameter: RobotAccountLastScannedTime;
  
  |TW Robot Service|
  :GetTWRobotUser();
  
  |ON_USER (SQL Server)|
  :Execute SP: **CTS_Customer_RobotListSel**;
  note right
    **Database**: ON_USER.wsv_cts
    **Timeout**: **900 seconds (15 minutes)** ⭐
    
    **Purpose**: Get TW-detected robot customers
    **Input**: Timespan (last scanned timestamp)
    
    **Query Logic**:
    ```sql
    -- Complex TW system query
    SELECT 
      CustId,
      Counter,
      Timestamp
    FROM TW_RobotDetection_Tables
    WHERE Timestamp > @lastScannedTimespan
    ORDER BY Timestamp
    ```
    
    **Data Source**: TW (Taiwan) System ⭐
    - Taiwan-specific rules
    - Manual/automated detection
    - Regional patterns
    
    **Returns**: TWRobotUserViewEntity
    - RobotUsers[] (CustId, Counter)
    - MaxTimestamp (pagination)
  end note
  
  :Return TWRobotUserViewEntity;
  
  |TW Robot Service|
  if (Has robots?) then (yes)
    :GetCustomerRole();
    |CTS_DataCenter (MySQL)|
    :Query Customer Roles;
    note right
      ```sql
      SELECT CustID, RoleID
      FROM CustomerMaster
      WHERE CustID IN (robot CustIDs)
      ```
      
      **RoleID**:
      - 1 = Member
      - Others = Agency
    end note
    
    |TW Robot Service|
    :GetRobotUserCategoryId();
    |CTS_DataCenter (MySQL)|
    :Query Robot CategoryID;
    note right
      ```sql
      SELECT CategoryID
      FROM CategoryMaster
      WHERE CategoryTypeName = 'ROBOTUSER'
      ```
    end note
    
    |TW Robot Service|
    :InsertTWRobotPackage();
    
    partition "Agency Robots (RoleID != 1)" {
      note right: **Agency Robot Path**
      :Filter Agency Robots;
      
      :Call Agency API;
      |External - Agency API|
      :POST /InsertTWRobotAgency;
      note right
        **Agency-Specific Handling**:
        - External routing
        - Agency API endpoint
        - Special agency rules
        - Batch processing
      end note
      
      |TW Robot Service|
      if (API failed?) then (yes)
        :Stop processing;
        stop
      endif
    }
    
    partition "Member Robots (RoleID == 1)" {
      note right: **Member Robot Path**
      :Filter Member Robots;
      :Chunk by internalSize;
      
      repeat
        :Transform to InsertProblemAccountEntity;
        
        :InsertProblemAccountPackage();
        |CTS_DataCenter (MySQL)|
        :INSERT INTO CTSCustomerClassification;
        note right
          **Insert Robot PA**:
          - CustID, CategoryID (Robot)
          - RoleID: 1 (Member)
          - Robot category
        end note
        
        :Return Inserted CustIDs;
        
        |TW Robot Service|
        :PushExternalPackageByCustId();
        |External - MainDB|
        :Push to MainDB API;
        
        |TW Robot Service|
        :Thread.Sleep(throttle);
        
      repeat while (More chunks?) is (yes)
      -> no;
    }
    
    |CTS_DataCenter (MySQL)|
    :Update System Parameter: RobotAccountLastScannedTime;
    note right
      ```sql
      UPDATE CTS_SystemParameter
      SET Value = MaxTimestamp
      WHERE ParameterKey = 'RobotAccountLastScannedTime'
      ```
    end note
  endif

end split

note right
  **Database Architecture**:
  
  **AI Robot Detection**:
  - **CTS_DataCenter** (MySQL): RobotDetection table + SystemParameter
  - **AI/ML System**: Populates RobotDetection with ML predictions
  - **Pagination**: RobotDetectionID (incremental ID)
  
  **TW Robot**:
  - **ON_USER** (SQL Server): TW system robot tables
  - **CTS_DataCenter** (MySQL): Customer roles + Robot category
  - **Pagination**: Timestamp (time-based)
  
  **Common Operations**:
  - **CTSCustomerClassification** (MySQL): Robot PA classification storage
  - **MainDB** (External): External visibility for all robots
  - **Throttling**: Thread.Sleep between chunks for both
  
  **Key Differences**:
  | Aspect | AI Robot | TW Robot |
  |--------|----------|----------|
  | Source DB | MySQL | SQL Server |
  | Pagination | ID-based | Time-based |
  | Timeout | 300s | 900s (15 min) |
  | Processing | Single path | Dual path (Agency + Member) |
  | Detection | Automated AI | Rule-based TW |
  
  **Performance Considerations**:
  - **AI Robot**: Fast queries, simple pagination
  - **TW Robot**: Complex queries, long timeout, dual routing
  - **Both**: Batch processing with throttling
  - **External Push**: Batched for efficiency
  
  **Error Handling**:
  - Failed insert → stop chunk processing
  - Failed push → return false, log error
  - Agency API failed (TW) → stop entire flow
  - Transactional integrity maintained
end note

|JobService|
:Complete;
stop

@enduml

